item.description:
@eyeownyew wrote:

[quote=“frozon566, post:3, topic:440980”]This happens when a program is compiled in a higher version of jdk than is trying to run it,

so if you were to say compile it in java 1.4 and then try to run in java 1.5, you would get this error, if you wouldn’t mind, upload the client and I’ll see if I can run it without any problems.[/quote]
It also happens when you’re using JDK 1.7 but it was compiled in JDK 1.6
